title: Four tourists found dead in vacation cabin in Maine
text:
Four tourists found dead in vacation cabin in Maine Adv: 
Jul 18, 2015 Adv: 
Four tourists on vacation from Massachusetts were found dead of apparent carbon monoxide poisoning at a holiday cabin in Maine. 
More details are not yet available
